{"tid":1757940,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]有啲咩好計可以18區區議會一齊做？","createTime":"2019-11-26T19:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T09:18:03.000Z","uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"de8a1700cf66062b10849327afc7be2efcda08f7","tid":1757940,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T19:16:59.000Z","msg":"大家一齊諗下 俾啲意見班手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我建議<br />\n1.18區消息及活動apps<br />\n2.細良建議嘅18區直播平台<br />\n3.互相招待其他區嘅本地一日遊團<br />\n介紹返自己社區<br />\n4. 同黃色經濟圈一齊搞活動<br />\n5. 嘗試由地區開始建立公投等等嘅民主機制<br />\n6. 一齊去保護 保育本土文化<br />\n搞返多啲本土活動<br />\n尤其是係吸引啲學生返完學之後參加啲文化活動<br />\n7. 建立由地區開始議政風氣<br />\n改變本身政府由上而下推政策嘅方式<br />\n8. 建立監察十八區區議會嘅民間機制<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79c94f93b949bb22a3d5551250915d8c50401d1","tid":1757940,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T23:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f93688613ad5cc26ef0bf0f8500aaba8eaadac8","tid":1757940,"uid":264138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T01:52:07.000Z","msg":"18區消息及活動apps<br />\n<a href=\"https://ourland.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fourland.hk&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx9wxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=58cadc90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ourland.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=hk.ourland.wall\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dhk.ourland.wall&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx9wxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=a37bcde2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=hk.ourland.wall</a>"},{"pid":"6683197e1ec97d36f43f96d40d97961ff2ed8e53","tid":1757940,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy